  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8073663/" class="title-link">边疆论</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8073663"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/72611050/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u72611050-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/72611050/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">圣卡奇亚诺</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-09-05"
      class="main-meta">2016-09-05 19:42:31</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8073663_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       边疆，是野蛮和文明的交汇点。 ——题记       美国历史很大程度上是对于大西部的扩殖史。       美国社会制度的独特之处在于，它们一直要适应人口膨胀带来的变化，这些变化是在移民穿越大陆，改造旷野，让边疆由原始的经济政治状态向复杂城市生活的蜕变进程中发生的。卡...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8073663_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8073663_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





